WEBVTT

00:00:00.398 --> 00:00:02.731
[His Holiness Pope Francis
Filmed in Vatican City

00:00:02.755 --> 00:00:05.436
First shown at TED Countdown
Global Launch, October 2020]

00:00:05.460 --> 00:00:06.610
Hello!

00:00:09.015 --> 00:00:10.889
We are living during a historic moment,

00:00:10.913 --> 00:00:14.466
marked by difficult challenges,
as we all know.

00:00:15.165 --> 00:00:17.673
The world is shaken by the crisis

00:00:17.697 --> 00:00:21.451
caused by the COVID-19 pandemic,

00:00:21.475 --> 00:00:22.760
which highlights

00:00:22.784 --> 00:00:27.012
another global challenge:

00:00:27.036 --> 00:00:30.265
the socio-environmental crisis.